edu.rice.comp440.rovers.model.percepts

Interface PerceptsFactory<PerceptsType extends IPercepts>

  • Type Parameters:
    PerceptsType - The specific subtype of IPercepts that this factory will make.

    public interface PerceptsFactory<PerceptsType extends IPercepts>
    The PerceptsFactory will make a Percepts class that is properly initialized to provide accurate percepts in the context of the current simulation state.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      PerceptsType make(AbstractRover<?> agent)
      Make a new instance of these Percepts, specifically initialized for agent's current state.
